    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this beauty is ready to hit the road with you! Everything runs smoothly, and I've taken great care of it over the years. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
