    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty car, and it's been such a fantastic ride. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved and maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It drives smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway. If you\u2019re looking for something dependable and high-quality without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 34500.0,
